40|$|This paper {{presents}} the design principles, architecture, implementation and performance ofourmodular key management protocol (MKMP) and an IP secure tunnel protocol (IPST) which protects the secrecy {{and integrity of}} IP <b>datagrams</b> using cryptographic functions. To use the existing IP infrastructure, MKMP is built on top of UDP and the IPST protocol is built by encapsulating IP <b>datagrams.</b> ...|$|R
